snippet.title: Curly Monkey 2 (Chinese plug & play console game)
snippet.description:
Curly Monkey is back oh yeah ♥ Curly Monkey is awesome and this game is awesome. You have to collect all the stars in each level and it's been a while since I played it so I lost all my lives before I found them all. OH WELL

System: VT03 / Developed by Nice Code / Recorded from DreamGear Motion Control 130 in 1 (NTSC)
